reviews.review_text: The Boyz at the beach! Surprised to be the first to review.  Garcia absolutely SHREDS the Fire seemingly from the top of the Mountain.  Even though there's some sloppiness, his earnestness shines through. Haven't heard this show in 15 years but remembered every note.
4.0 stars See my review of the Scotton/Walker/Miller SBD. This is the best AUD, but that's not really saying much. Good show, not great.
